<refentry id="bif.Basis" xreflabel="Basis">

<refmeta>
<indexterm>
<primary>Basis</primary>
</indexterm>

<refentrytitle>Basis</refentrytitle>
<refmiscinfo>Built-in function</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
<refname>Basis</refname>
<refpurpose>
Creates a basis for an extensive form game
</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
Basis[efg->EFG] =: EFBASIS
</synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1><title>Description</title>
<para>
<function>Basis</function> creates and returns a new basis for
the game <parameter>efg</parameter>.  The basis contains all nodes and
all actions in the game.
</para>
</refsect1>

